The local server is started with staticExpress.js.
The website runs on localhost:10000

The json files inside the json folder can be changed and the bot will notice the changed after restarting the server.

The main json file is minecraft_biomes.json.
It works with dictionaries. Those must follow a specific order:
intent -> keywords
answer -> answers the bot gives for the keywords
question -> questions the bot asks if he doesn't understand
list -> sublist of the intent with more dictionaries.

The bot logic is in bot.js
botti.js is for user join and hello messages.
